# Override global .gitignore to track .kiro/specs/ only
# Pattern explanation:
#   1. !/.kiro/         - First, negate .kiro/ itself (undo global ignore)
#   2. /.kiro/*         - Then ignore all contents of .kiro/
#   3. !/.kiro/specs/   - Finally, negate .kiro/specs/ (make it trackable)
!/.kiro/
/.kiro/*
!/.kiro/specs/
